context: "LLM Observability Forecast Feature"
description: "Handles time-series forecasting for cost and latency models, computing budget breach risks and forecast summaries."
dependencies:
  clickhouse: "Clickhouse is used to fetch raw cost/latency series data."
  redis: "Redis is used for low-latency caching of computed forecast results."
  postgres: "Postgres stores long-term forecasts and defines budget limits."
  timesfm: "TimesFM is a foundational model used for forecasting time series."
networking_criticality: "High. Clickhouse and Redis are on critical paths for sub-second API lookups."
